(firstQuint)MammoSite as Sole Radiation Therapy Technique for Ductal Carcinoma In-Situ.

 Data relevant to the evaluation of the efficacy and safety of the MammoSite RTS system in providing radiation therapy to patients with DCIS will be collected.

 The MammoSite is a radionuclide applicator designed to deliver internal radiation therapy (brachytherapy) in patients with breast tumors following breast tumor resection surgery (lumpectomy).

